  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Simon and her daughter, because they apparently left London once the air raids started, and I didn't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I wrote to the old address, and I don't know if it was forwarded.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I just, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Again, you know, my father did not tell me of the conditions in that camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were-- it's perhaps a form of resistance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And you know, normally, we think of resistance that you pick up a weapon, and you fight, you go up on the barricades.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But there's another way of resisting, and I think both my parents resisted passively in that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
